org.matsim.counts.algorithms

Class CountsComparisonAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.counts.algorithms.CountsComparisonAlgorithm

  • public class CountsComparisonAlgorithm
extends Object
    This algorithm can be used to obtain a List of CountSimComparison objects from the LinkAttributes of a run. A time filter can be specified.
    Author:
    dgrether
